features: Two In One Toy Cars: Combined with car and robot, this RC transformer car could transform automatically from car to robot back and forth fluently when you press the button on the remote control. Keep your child entertained with the toy that never gets old - cruise down the streets in a drifting sports car or man the battlefield with an intergalactic robot.

One Button Transformation & Automatic Demonstration: When you press the button on the right, this RC drift car will switch smoothly from the car to the robot form, which is easy to switch back and forth. The automatic demonstration function will bring you surprises!! The unique universal wheel design allows you to enjoy 360-degree rotation and drift, forward & backward are very simple and easy to operate.

Multiplayer Combat Fun: Equipped with cool LED police lights and perfect size, our RC cars for kids bring the most realistic experience. The 2.4G Hz remote control technology ensures that there will be no signal interference between each car, so parents and children or children themselves can use different cars to play together happily.

Safe & Durable: This remote control robot car is made of durable ABS plastic material, non-toxic, durable, and safe for kids. The anti-fall car body is strong and resistant to fall and deal with a variety of barbaric children's operations, ensuring your kids have lasting and happy entertainment.

Perfect Gift for Kids: With a cool box package, this excellent transform RC car is a perfect toy for boys and girls who are obsessed with robots and cars/police cars. Ideal gift for kids’ birthday, Christmas, or other festivals. Strong warranty, for any problem you suffered, please contact seller directly first, we will solve it perfectly for you.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 11, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Simple and Effective.
reviews.reviewText: This toy car/transformer is for our four year old. The buttons are simple, forward/back and turn. One button makes the “transformer” stand up and the car is still drivable. Only issue is the transform button is a continuous motion so you have to guess where to stop it, sort of like wiper blades on your car if you just turn off the ignition while they are in motion. My kid loves to show off the moves and drive it around our hard floors, not as successful on carpet. We only have the one so no comment on the 2.4Ghz interference. Rechargeable batteries for the car with a USB cord and 2 AA for the remote. Received 1/10/2024.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Wonderful gift for a toddler
reviews.reviewText: We gifted this product to a toddler. He enjoyed it immensely. The product is working in good condition and is safe for 5 year old to use

I am so happy with this toy car! My 5-year-old cousin loved it and can't stop playing with it. He especially loves the transformer. I also requested a birthday note in the package, and the sender had no problem with sending it. The gift also arrived very quickly in advance!So worth it especially for younger kids!

The car is smaller than expected for the price. It has poor control. When transforming your robot and to car, you have to hold onto a button continuously and let go at the right time or it will “over-transform” and become in-between car and robot. No on/off button for remote. Manual says light will go off after fully charged which should take about 120min but light still on after 5 hours. Poor quality product.
